---
// About.astro — Phase 3
---

<section id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label">About</p>
    <p class="about-text">
      I've spent a decade hunting unauthorized sellers, dismantling grey market
      networks, and building the enforcement programs that keep distribution
      clean. The work sits at the edge of compliance and commercial operations —
      MAP enforcement, anti-diversion strategy, authorized reseller frameworks —
      and I like it there.
    </p>
    <p class="about-subtext">
      These projects are tools I've built to do that work at scale.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  #about {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: var(--size-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-text {
    font-size: var(--size-lg);
    max-width: 620px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .about-subtext {
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
    font-size: var(--size-base);
    color: var(--color-subtle);
    max-width: 620px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
</style>
